# Citrix receiver repackaging

Download Citriy Receiver .deb package from 
[https://www.citrix.com/downloads/citrix-receiver/linux/receiver-for-linux-latest.html]:
> Debian Packages 
>   → Full Packages (Self-Service Support) 
>   → Receiver for Linux (x86_64)

## Why repackaing?

* Don't install to /opt/Citrix/ICAClient but /usr/lib/ICAClient
* Use system-wide /etc/ssl/certs from ca-certificates as the certificate store
* Put config in /etc/icaclient
